    "These datasets a sampled from the BIRD benchmark (Li et al., 2023), which 2 The value of τ h has been experimentally determined at 0.9 to ensure rigorous hallucination removal.",
    "is composed from real data sources spanning 37 domains (Volvovsky et al., 2024).",
    "We focus on a subset rather than the entire database benchmark to manage costs, as the correctness evaluation requires specialized human judgment.",
    "In the sampling process, we ensured thematic and structural variety across the databases by including:",
    "• california_schools: education data in the state of California; it has 3 tables with 11-49 columns (median of 29)."
